children.text: There are several minor shrinkage cracks (~1.5mm wide) in this slab, which should be monitored over the next 24 months to confirm whether there is any structural movement.
NOTE : This is not an action item. We are simply documenting the shrinkage cracks to assist with the monitoring process, should it ever be required.

It should be noted that it does not appear to be anything more than shrinkage cracks at this stage, however the owners should monitor these areas with reference to table 2.10 above, and notify the builder of any changes.
